name: Cat-in-a-Box Ether
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: Cat-in-a-Box is a lending protocol that self-stabilises by incentivising the conversion of debt from users with unhealthy loans into buying pressure for the system's borrowable asset. This process supports the value of the soft-pegged synthetic asset to ensure it remains attractive to borrow.
